                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Ouvrez ! » — Qui frappe à l’heure\nOù l’homme dort souvent ?\nEst-ce un blessé qui pleure\nDe revenir vivant ?\n— « Ouvrez ! je vous en prie ;\nDe mon lointain hameau,\nJ’apporte à la patrie\nCe que j’ai de plus beau."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "« Des anges sentinelles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Envolés sans remords,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "J’ai vu les blanches ailes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Envelopper vos morts !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Regardez ! Nulles toiles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
