                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ils n’ont pas de linceuls ! »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Des anges sentinelles,\nEnvolés sans remords,\nJ’ai vu les blanches ailes\nEnvelopper vos morts !\nRegardez ! Nulles toiles\nNe doublent leurs cercueils ;\nPitié, jette tes voiles !\nIls n’ont pas de linceuls ! »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et la femme au front d’ange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Aux yeux tristes sans pleurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "De la terre où tout change",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Essayant les douleurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Au nom du Dieu qui donne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
