                    "line_text": "Sur de chastes autels",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Apporte une humble aumône",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "À ses frères mortels !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et la femme au front d’ange,\nAux yeux tristes sans pleurs,\nDe la terre où tout change\nEssayant les douleurs,\nAu nom du Dieu qui donne,\nSur de chastes autels\nApporte une humble aumône\nÀ ses frères mortels !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "« Je suis… je fus promise",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "À qui défend vos dieux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Mais la noce est remise :",
