                    "line_text": "On se retrouve aux cieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Cet anneau qui me lie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Entraînera mon cœur :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "C’est le don de ma vie !…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Qu’il vous porte bonheur. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Je suis… je fus promise\nÀ qui défend vos dieux ;\nMais la noce est remise :\nOn se retrouve aux cieux !\nCet anneau qui me lie\nEntraînera mon cœur :\nC’est le don de ma vie !…\nQu’il vous porte bonheur. »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Et, comme la colombe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Vient d’un autre séjour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
