                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Sur un drapeau sanglant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "La jeune vierge veuve",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Posa l’anneau tremblant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et, comme la colombe\nVient d’un autre séjour,\nJeter sur une tombe\nQuelque secret d’amour,\nFidèle à son épreuve,\nSur un drapeau sanglant\nLa jeune vierge veuve\nPosa l’anneau tremblant."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Ces dons que le cœur sème",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Aux blessés du chemin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Dieu les voit, Dieu les aime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
